                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9429" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-1424</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">787 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">从“小飞象”到比萨帝国：尊宝比萨的获客之道</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">From &quot;Little Flying Elephant&quot; to Pizza Empire: The Customer Acquisition Strategy of Champion Pizza</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">王创，陈建伶，范雪竹，王韶珊</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">华南理工大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">杭州千尊饮食连锁有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">17 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">尊宝比萨；市场定位；客户价值主张</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Champion Pizza; Market Positioning; Customer Value Proposition</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随着中国经济快速发展和国际化程度加深，西式连锁餐饮品牌纷纷进入中国市场，本土品牌如尊宝比萨也迅速崛起。自1998年成立以来，尊宝比萨以中低端市场为目标，逐步扩大规模，至2025年已拥有超过3000家门店，尤其在广东省市场占据领先地位。然而，中国餐饮业在经历了四十多年的高速发展后，市场规模增长乏力，行业竞争愈发激烈，产品同质化问题日益凸显。在此背景下，尊宝比萨如何通过精准的市场定位和客户价值主张，实现持续增长并保持优势地位？本案例通过分析尊宝比萨发展壮大的历程，深入探讨其市场定位和客户价值主张的成功之处，为餐饮品牌在竞争激烈的市场中保持生存与发展提供借鉴和启发。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With the rapid development of China&#39;s economy and increasing internationalization, many Western chain restaurant brands have entered the Chinese market, while local chain restaurant brands, such as Champion Pizza, have also risen quickly. Since its establishment in 1998, Champion Pizza has targeted the mid- to low-end market and gradually expanded its scale, reaching over 3,000 stores by 2025, with a particularly strong market presence in Guangdong Province. However, after more than forty years of rapid growth in China&#39;s catering industry, market growth has slowed, industry competition has intensified and product homogenization has become increasingly prominent. In this context, how can Champion Pizza achieve sustained growth and maintain a competitive edge through precise market positioning and customer value propositions? This study analyzes Champion Pizza&#39;s growth trajectory to explore the successes of its market positioning and customer value propositions, thereby providing insights and inspiration for restaurant brands striving to survive and thrive in a fiercely competitive market.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《市场营销》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STP市场定位；客户价值主张</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-03</td>
                            </tr>
